'''克雷格·比爾科'''（'''Craig Bierko'''，{{bd|1964年|8月18日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位[[演員|演員]]和[[歌手|歌手]]。比爾科出生在紐約州<ref name="filmr">{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/8/Craig-Bierko.html |title=Craig Bierko Film Reference biography |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909081415/http://www.filmreference.com/film/8/Craig-Bierko.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1964/08/23/births.html?_r=0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021190645/http://www.nytimes.com/1964/08/23/births.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他的母親是一位改信天主教的猶太人，比爾科非常自豪他的猶太血統<ref name="Bierko">{{cite news|last=Lipton|first=Brian Scott|title=MODERN MAN|publisher=TheaterMania|date=2004-12-02|url=http://www.theatermania.com/content/news.cfm/story/5396|accessdate=2006-12-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210092411/http://www.theatermania.com/content/news.cfm/story/5396|archivedate=2007-02-10|df=}}<br>"My mother is Jewish, though she converted to Catholicism," Bierko says, "so we ended up being Christmas tree Jews. I grew up in Westchester with a lot of Jewish friends, and I feel very connected to that part of my heritage. When I read the play, it was the first time I'd seen that part of myself addressed."<br></ref> His surname is Polish.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/MrCraigBierko/status/337473163321569280 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2016-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418040540/https://twitter.com/mrcraigbierko/status/337473163321569280 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾就讀於波士頓大學<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1989-10-23/features/8901240682_1_chicago-international-film-festival-movie-cycles |title=Acting Cycle |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2016-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605095703/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1989-10-23/features/8901240682_1_chicago-international-film-festival-movie-cycles |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/6122/Craig-Bierko/biography |title=Craig Bierko biography |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305145126/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/6122/Craig-Bierko/biography |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

